data.description: Perfect lock and leave in desirable Leander Schools.  Do you want to spend your free time not taking care of the yard?  This condo lives like a single family home and, the HOA mows, trims and mulches the yard.  This 4 bedroom home also features a loft-gameroom space upstairs and a dedicated media room.  The media room is ideal for a social media influencer or work from home person.  The built in bar adds a fun entertaining feature.  Features such as wrought iron balusters, 36" cabinets, 6" trim board, granite counters, stainless appliances and more create a sophisticated feel to this open concept condo. The kitchen is spacious and has a breakfast bar, eat in kitchen and large pantry. The condo complex backs to a city owned green space with access to hike and bike trail and Brushy Creek.  The complex is super convenient to retail and restaurants.  And the backyard is primed for a deck add on to expand the outdoor fun.
